I just want to be able to sit down, spend some hours googling programming commissions gigs, and be done with it. I just want to do something that gets me to where I want to be. I'm getting sick of being helpless to my own causes and others causes all the time.

I don't want to waste any more of my time playing video games like Factorio, Slime Rancher, watching Youtube videos... Tweeting. On this platform. I try not to, but it's the only motivation that strikes me.
